
I use /services as the root of service instances. I am not the first one: DJ Bernstein already advocated /service in daemontools (https://cr.yp.to/daemontools/faq/create.html#why)

create service.cfg


Apache
------

Create service config (config/apache2/mkservice_conf)

Create apache config (config/apache2/mkhttpd_conf)

Copy envvars file (config/apache2/envvars -> etc/apache2)
